        </links>
        <content><![CDATA[<p>Before chaining gets possible, you have to <a href="%(link0)">create a new sitemap master configuration file</a> and have to define the master configuration definitions to start with. You can either start with one master configuration, e.g., with the Mercury standard master configuration as shown below, or with a combination of several master configurations as shown in the example of the <a href="%(link1)">last chapter</a>.</p>]]></content>
