          </link>
        </Image>
        <Title><![CDATA[Customized Mercury Master Configuration]]></Title>
      </Image>
    </Section>
    <Section>
      <Text name="Text0">
        <links/>
        <content><![CDATA[<p>The master configurations at the very beginning of the <strong><em>Content elements</em></strong> tab represent the stock of definitions to which chaining techniques can be applied.</p>]]></content>
      </Text>
